title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 29 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 29 2022
description:
Florida Governor Ron DeSantis talks with Clay and Buck, responds to Disney on their criticism of the parental rights in education bill, stand against transgender swimmer, Biden's airline mask mandate, mass migration to Florida. Kyrie Irving stands up for freedom. Poll: Trump Trounces Biden or Harris in 2024. C&B take a call from a man in his RV moving to Florida. Taxing unrealized gains is a stupid, unworkable idea. The Top Gun: Maverick trailer is out.
